ğŸ“„ Overview
This project uses a Logistic Regression model trained on credit-card transactions. Users enter an amount, pick a currency and time unit, and the app predicts whether the transaction is fraudulent, with confidence and risk level. It also keeps a downloadable audit history.

ğŸ§  Machine Learning Details
Logistic Regression with class weighting for imbalance

StandardScaler for feature scaling

Percentile-based high-amount warning

Outputs a calibrated fraud probability

